defaultOn many occasions people contacting us had not completed their landlord's internal 
defaultcomplaints procedure (ICP). In most cases we used to advise completion of the ICP 
defaultbecause the. former Scheme provided that, usually, the Ombudsman would not 
defaultconsider complaints which in his opinion could still be pursued through providers' procedures.
defaultUnde
defaultr the new Scheme the value that we can add in these circumstances is even 
