defaultthe Local Government Ombudsmen (LGO) may consult during the course of their investigations. It also provides that if, 
defaultat any stage in the course of conducting an investigation, I form the opinion that the 
defaultcomplaint relates partly to a matter which could be
default the subject of an investigation by 
defaultthe LGO, I must consult with the appropriate 'Commissioner' about the complaint 
defaultand, if I consider it necessary, inform the complainant of the steps necessary to 
defaultinitiate a complaint with the LGO.
defaultProvision is also made 
defaultto enable me and the LGO to carry out joint investigations. In 
