defaultopinion that the complaint relates partly to a matter within the jurisdiction of the LGO, 
defaultI defaultmay conduct an investigation jointly with the LGO provided I have first obtained the 
defaultconsent of the complainant or the complainant's representative. Moreover, if I form the opinion that a complaint which is being investigated by the LGO relates partly to 
defaulta
