defaultCommon principlesdefaultThe Directive states that effective ADR procedures should be guided by a number of 
defaultcommon principles, such as impartiality, transparency, effectivene
defaultss, and fairness. 
defaultNo ombudsman in the UK or Ireland will disagree with this statement except to say 
