defaultIt seems to me that where reports are 
defaultlaid before Parliament they are documents of 
defaultpublic record and this requirement should be enough to meet the requirements of the 
defaultDirective. Equally, the public availability of such reports should be enough to enable:
default" the competent authorities to publish regular reports on the development and 
defaultfunctioning of ADR entities. Every three years, the Commission will report to 
defaultthe European Parliament and the Council on the application of the Directive".
